      "value": "Strengthen institutional capacity of education service providers (govt and non govt)  in the  DACAW, Urban Areas, Education Focused districts.\r\nTechnical assistance to develop a roll out plan for CFS initiatives in the ECD, School and   alternative provision centers in UNICEF supported education districts (DACAW/GE districts and targeted Urban Areas)\r\n\r\nDevelop UNICEF strategy to address the specific education  needs and  issues of Terai and  Far and Mid West Region\r\nLobby,  advocacy and capacity development to ensure CGD friendly WASH facilities  contributing to  fulfillment of minimum standard for a child friendly schools, ECD centers   in all situations.  ( In coordination with WASH section)"
    },
